PrecisAppointment of RICHARD BELLIVEAU as High Commissioner for Canada to Brunei Darussalam; DENIS BRIAND as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Guinea; GRAHAM GREEN as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Croatia; LOUISE OUIMET as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Burkina-Faso; BRIAN SCHUMACHER as High Commissioner for Canada to the Commonwealth of Australia, with concurrent accreditation as High Commissioner for Canada to Solomon Islands and High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Vanuatu; NANCY STILES as Ambassador of Canada to the Federative Republic of Brazil; ALAN VIRTUE as Consul General of Canada in Sydney; and CHRIS WESTDAL as Ambassador of Canada to Ukraine.
